      <div class="excellence-content">
        <h2>Born From Ritual, Designed For Excellence</h2>
        <p>
          LUMA Heritage is rooted in the elegance of ancestral beauty rituals—where care is a ceremony, and ingredients are revered.
          We translate this heritage into modern luxury formulas designed to meet the standards of high-end hotels, spas, and concept stores.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          We believe skincare should feel like a refined ritual: sensorial, precise, and quietly powerful.
          Every texture, every note, every finish is designed to elevate the experience—without excess, without noise.
        </p>

        <h2>Made For Premium Partners</h2>
        <p>
          LUMA is developed to integrate seamlessly into premium environments: in-room amenities, spa treatments, and curated retail selections.
          If you’re building a luxury guest experience, LUMA becomes part of your signature.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 18px;">
          Explore the ingredient story on <a href="elixir.html" style="text-decoration: underline;">Elixir – The Secret of Dates</a>,
